{"tid":306840,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"鋤大D技巧討論","createTime":"2017-07-03T00:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T01:02:29.000Z","uid":27388,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01126f5c90ce892ae1a66b4e12029718ac894e9b","tid":306840,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:49:19.000Z","msg":"點解有d人揸咩牌總係贏，一係就輸少，點都唔俾人炒，手機game-神來也鋤大d都係輸多贏少，有冇高手分享下技術指導下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2194932560544e21c14b3410bd1e333eac2aa39","tid":306840,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ec5210d1e06a762dce945865f674753d5fa898","tid":306840,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:52:13.000Z","msg":"扣牌"},{"pid":"459dc73f40a392f7d95ee2b448eb5c96555e3fad","tid":306840,"uid":66951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:59:01.000Z","msg":"由最大個隻打落去"},{"pid":"11c53553eda4f6405f428175b225a33bca878fa7","tid":306840,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:59:50.000Z","msg":"用降龍十八掌"},{"pid":"e52b2a02d4a3a16fd5b0b27e55627bdc1676efc4","tid":306840,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"猶大打起"},{"pid":"4156b9e819422593460cf8e07fdbedbf9a9b1a85","tid":306840,"uid":101417,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:11:37.000Z","msg":"我玩長途dee次次都贏（限於朋友玩）<br />\n不外乎<br />\n靚牌-》盡量炒人<br />\n廢牌-》唔好比人炒<br />\n<br />\n出牌就唔好一定最細打起<br />\n輸左唔好比人睇自己重有咩牌<br />\n低手渣靚牌個樣通常好凝重，所以靚牌廢牌要一個樣比人睇<br />\n幾靚都好唔好渣死諗住出5隻，唔對路就要放棄<br />\n四個人玩自己無其一個數字就知有一最小有一pair<br />\n<br />\n不能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc7e722772ad252c32932a0ca6202e0c2623e31","tid":306840,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:17:13.000Z","msg":"我都係贏多輸少  longrun鋤一定贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515e100fd7614e59451af88771a181a62d3e3e45","tid":306840,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係贏多輸少  longrun鋤一定贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n背牌，知道有咩牌未出<br />\n背埋每個人每次出牌順序，可以推測出每個人仲有咩牌<br />\n每次人地出牌，觀察每個人放牌的位置習慣，例如有d人鍾意順序由細至大放，有d人鍾意將五條放哂在右邊，就可以好容易估到佢淨翻咩牌"},{"pid":"837289d45ab4d3167f09736ff81d10df358bfa6f","tid":306840,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c47ce909050298e138d9192d8233a9b6267dc5b","tid":306840,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"936da99bb184201303eeac8d664127f6dd3aaa8e","tid":306840,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:51:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aec1e873bb9e0d4f413ee3be113b5fc3b63fbd9a","tid":306840,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我玩長途dee次次都贏（限於朋友玩）<br />\n不外乎<br />\n靚牌-》盡量炒人<br />\n廢牌-》唔好比人炒<br />\n<br />\n出牌就唔好一定最細打起<br />\n輸左唔好比人睇自己重有咩牌<br />\n低手渣靚牌個樣通常好凝重，所以靚牌廢牌要一個樣比人睇<br />\n幾靚都好唔好渣死諗住出5隻，唔對路就要放棄<br />\n四個人玩自己無其一個數字就知有一最小有一pair<br />\n<br />\n不能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4b8e3cfd41c90beb4fef2ea98b94129135b522","tid":306840,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:02:29.000Z","msg":"靚牌就博結<